Device-Delcom-VSI version 0.05

The files and code here are supporting the use of the Delcom Engineering
(www.delcom-eng.com) USB Visual Indicator device under Linux with libusb
and Perl.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install



DEPENDENCIES

None.


